# Canvas Assignments Panel Mod

A Tampermonkey userscript that adds a draggable panel to Canvas, showing:
- Missing assignments
- Upcoming assignments (next 7 days)
- Overdue assignments (excluding announcements)

---

##  English Instructions

### Installation
1. Install the Tampermonkey extension:
   - [Tampermonkey for Edge](https://microsoftedge.microsoft.com/addons/detail/tampermonkey/iikmkjmpaadaobahmlepeloendndfphd)
   - [Tampermonkey for Chrome](https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/tampermonkey/dhdgffkkebhmkfjojejmpbldmpobfkfo)
   - [Tampermonkey for Firefox](https://addons.mozilla.org/firefox/addon/tampermonkey/)

2. Once Tampermonkey is installed, click the **Raw** link for [`assignments-panel.user.js`](./assignments-panel.user.js).

3. Tampermonkey will prompt you to install the script. Click **Install**.

4. Go to your Canvas dashboard (`udem.instructure.com`) and click the new **Assignments Panel** button.

### Updates
- When you publish new versions, bump the `@version` number in the script header.
- If you set `@updateURL` and `@downloadURL` to the Raw link of this file, Tampermonkey will auto-update for users.

