##  Release Notes

### v1.0
- Initial release
- Panel shows Missing, Upcoming, and Overdue assignments
- Panel is draggable and can be toggled with a button 
- Only works on dashboard (tablero) right now 
- To see earlier or later assignments you will have to drag the page up and down.

### v1.1 (planned)
- Improved date parsing for localized formats
- Option to customize upcoming window (e.g., 14 days instead of 7)
- Styling tweaks for better readability
